a arha vyaadhi is a type of Ayurvedic treatment that is used to prevent the spread of poison. This can be done through a variety of methods, such as herbal remedies, detoxification, and yoga. Visha prasara nirodhaka arha vyaadhi is used to treat a variety of conditions, including poisoning, infection, and chronic disease."}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["tag", "file_path", "file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b84a990e-31e4-4e9c-aac3-bfb6c54af261", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "/home/dai/rag/data/clean_html/Therapeutic_Procedures/Proc_Agnikarma.html", "file_name": "Proc_Agnikarma.html", "file_type": "text/html", "file_size": 9574, "creation_date": "2024-02-15", "last_modified_date": "2024-02-14", "last_accessed_date": "2024-02-15"}, "hash": "e2a67aec347ac462a1fd64b8b3e053bb800a0ea7489939ee6acf077beb03b371", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "text": "Agnikarma  Chikitsaa Karma,Agni Karma Specific Classification,Visha Upakrama Specific Classification,Vran`a Upakrama Instruments used,Ajaa S`hakrit Instruments used,Godanta Instruments used,Gud`a Instruments used,Jambvausht`haadi Loha S`halaakaa Instruments used,Kshaudra Instruments used,Pancha Dhaatu S`halaakaa Instruments used,Pippali Instruments used,S`halaakaa Instruments used,S`hara Instruments used,Sneha Karma,S`hon`itasthaapana Karma,S`hoolapras`hamana Karma,Visha Prasara Nirodhaka Arha Vyaadhi Prakaara,Vaataja Vyaadhi Arha Vyaadhi,Apachee Arha Vyaadhi,Apachee --) Amarmajaata Apakva Apachee Arha Vyaadhi,Arbuda --) Medoja Arbuda Arha Vyaadhi,Ars`ha Arha Vyaadhi,Ars`ha --) Avasthaa --) Atyartha Nirgata + Doshapoorn`a Arha Vyaadhi,Ars`ha --) Avasthaa --) Karkas`ha + Sthira + Prithu + Kathin`a Ars`ha Arha Vyaadhi,Ars`ha --) Avasthaa --) Mahaan Ars`ha + Balavaan Rugn`a Arh