* Facial disorders, such as acne or inflammation.\n- **Naasaa Roga:** Nasal disorders, such as sinusitis.\n- **Netra Roga:** Eye disorders, such as conjunctivitis.\n- **Raajayakshmaa:** Tuberculosis.\n- **S'hiroroga:** Head disorders, such as migraines.\n- **S'hleepada:** Paralysis.\n- **S'hooka Roga:** Swelling of the scrotum.\n- **S'hoola:** Abdominal pain.\n- **S'hotha:** Swelling.\n- **S'hvaasa:** Asthma.\n- **Stambha:** Stiffness.\n- **Sthaanabhedena Graha:** Localized pain.\n- **Stree Roga:** Gynecological disorders.\n- **Udara (Kaphaja):** Ascites caused by excess Kapha.\n- **Vaatarakta:** Gout.\n- **Vaatavyaadhi:** Vata-related disorders, such as arthritis or neuralgia.\n- **Vidradhi:** Abscesses.\n- **Visha Roga:** Poisoning.\n- **Vran'a:** Wounds.\n- **Vran'as'hotha:** Inflammation of wounds.\n- **Vriddhi (Vaataja):** Enlargement caused by excess Vata."}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["tag", "file_path", "file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "a5cd4fb4-eec2-47e2-9d82-0c97d37318dc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "/home/dai/rag/data/clean_html/Therapeutic_Procedures/Proc_Upanaaha_Sveda.html", "file_name": "Proc_Upanaaha_Sveda.html", "file_type": "text/html", "file_size": 6692, "creation_date": "2024-02-15", "last_modified_date": "2024-02-14", "last_accessed_date": "2024-02-15"}, "hash": "97c8d69b4bfc14945ac932335a5684218945792b683ea886016cb644932bb565", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "text": "Upanaaha Sveda  Chikitsaa Karma,Upanaaha Sveda Specific Classification,Svedana Gun`a,Teekshn`a Gun`a,Ushn`a Karma,S`hoolapras`hamana Karma,S`hothahara Karma,Svedana Arha Vyaadhi Prakaara,Kaphaja Vyaadhi Arha Vyaadhi Prakaara,Vaataja Vyaadhi Arha Vyaadhi,Aamavaata Arha Vyaadhi,Arbuda --) Pittaja Arbuda Arha Vyaadhi,Arbuda --)