 bed and twice as deep as its width is dug. This place should be suitable (Pras`hasta) and not exposed to wind. It should be filled with excreta of elephant, horses, cows, donkeys, or camels. This should be ignited. When the material is completely burnt out and smokeless fire remains a bed should be placed over this pit.\n\n* **Patient preparation:** Body massage.\n\n**Pradhaan karma:**\n\n* The patient lies on the bed and receives the fomentation therapy.\n\n**Other Description:**\n\n* Prakaara Paribhaashaa is a type of fomentation therapy that is used to treat a variety of conditions, including pain, stiffness, and inflammation.\n* It is a safe and effective treatment that can be used in conjunction with other Ayurvedic therapies.\n\n**Terminology:**\n\n* **Fomentation:** The application of heat or cold to the body to relieve pain and inflammation.\n* **Pras`hasta:** Suitable or appropriate.\n* **Pradhaan karma:** The main treatment.\n\nI hope this summary is helpful. Please let me know if you have any other questions."}}, "423a026e-69a9-4ab3-85c5-5c7d3ad5c2ef": {"node_ids": ["9ff0edb2-f8de-4449-bfb6-5a50b9cbbdc4"], "metadata": {"tag": "p", "file_path": "/home/dai/rag/data/clean_html/Therapeutic_Procedures/Procedure_Files/Krimighna.htm", "file_name": "Krimighna.htm", "file_type": "text/html", "file_size": 894, "creation_date": "2024-02-15", "last_modified_date": "2024-02-14", "last_accessed_date": "2024-02-15", "summary": "I apologize, but the context you provided does not contain any information on 'Pradhaanakarma' or any other relevant details. Therefore, I cannot summarize the requested information from the provided context."}}, "9f927fc5-f945-46c4-a332-74876bd41e44": {"node_ids": ["8ac80c65-3556-43f5-ba29-e1b4962c6ca3"], "metadata": {"tag": "p", "file_path": "/home/dai/rag/data/clean_html/Therapeutic_Procedures/Procedure_Files/Krishn`ikaran`a.htm", "file_name": "Krishn`ikaran`a.htm", "file_type": "text/html", "file_size": 511, "creation_date": "2024-02-15", "l